text: Always dependably perfect mani and pedi! Lovely staff, fresh product and clean environment. A quick get away and perfect result. Normal , gel, French and elaborate…

Kiki is the nail queen! After many failed attempts to get acrylics, I finally found a gem! Kiki suggested ‘strengthened’ and I haven’t looked back! I won’t let anyone else in SG near my nails! Salon is spotless, girls are so friendly and while it’s not the cheapest, you get what you pay for!

I had a wonderful first experience when I got my facial done at this outlet. My beautician was Yen and she really looked after me well and made me comfortable. I highly recommend her to anyone out there looking for a relaxing facial session. She is also very warm and friendly!

Finally I found a perfect place for gel nails. Fully recommend, I love to go to Kiki, always put so much attention and effort to make my nails perfect. But the most important, gel nails stay sooo long.

This is my go-to place for manicures and pedicures and it’s always such lovely experience. I recently had an amazing facial with Yen – she was great and my skin felt amazing afterwards. Highly recommended and I will definitely do it again.
